CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, January 10, 1953, pg. 12 reads: "The Escorts...The handsome young men who guided the debutantes through the presentation waltz, the tango and grand march, smile for the cameraman."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of twenty-three debutante escorts wearing tuxedos and light colored bow ties, including three kneeling in front, posed in Syria Mosque for 1953 Alpha Kappa Alpha cotillion
